### Get all products
GET http://localhost/product/all

### Add a product
POST http://localhost/product/add
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "razor",
    "price": 99,
    "stock": 100
}

### Update a product
PUT http://localhost/product/update
{
    "id": 1,
    "name": "product name",
    "price": 119,
    "stock": 1000
}

### Delete a product
DELETE http://localhost/product/delete/1